&lt;p&gt;these attributes so as to meet the requirements of fairness at work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;126&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communicate Effectively&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;342&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Be able to contribute effectively to meetings and present information in a&lt;/p&gt;
